OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FThe parents of two teenage girls
OL,8,Fkilled in the Hillsborough disaster
OL,9,Fsay they welcome a promise from a
OL,10,Fchief constable to correct the record
OL,11,Frelating to their deaths.
OL,13,FVictoria Hicks, 15, and her 19-year-
OL,14,Fold sister Sarah were among the 97
OL,15,FLiverpool supporters who died
OL,16,Ffollowing the Hillsborough disaster at
OL,17,Fthe FA Cup semi-final on April 15 1989.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
