PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FTheir parents, Jenni and Trevor Hicks,
OL,8,Fhave been campaigning to correct
OL,9,Fofficial court records ` which wrongly
OL,10,Fstate the sisters lost consciousness
OL,11,Fwithin 30 seconds and died a short
OL,12,Ftime later.
OL,14,FThe Hillsborough Independent Panel
OL,15,Freport, published in 2012, and new
OL,16,Finquests, which concluded the victims
OL,17,Fwere unlawfully killed, found the
OL,18,Fsuggestion victims lost consciousness
OL,19,Fwithin seconds was flawed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FBut records cannot be officially
OL,8,Fcorrected without the consent of South
OL,9,FYorkshire Police (SYP).
OL,11,FOn Thursday, a spokesman for Mr and Ms
OL,12,FHicks said they had met Chief
OL,13,FConstable Lauren Poultney, who
OL,14,Fconfirmed she had instructed the
OL,15,Fforce's legal team to proceed with a
OL,16,Fstatement in open court acknowledging
OL,17,Fthat earlier court findings should be
OL,18,Fcorrected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FMs Hicks, who is originally from
OL,8,FYorkshire but now lives in Liverpool,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This is the first time we have
OL,10,Fsat down with a chief constable and
OL,11,Fbeen told directly that steps will be
OL,12,Ftaken to correct the record about our
OL,13,Fdaughters."
OL,15,F"We welcome what we have been told
OL,16,Ftoday, and we are pleased that South
OL,17,FYorkshire Police appears to recognise
OL,18,Fthat this needs to be put right."
OL,26,@qD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,F"But after everything families have
OL,8,Fbeen through over the past 36 years,
OL,9,Fwe will wait to see it happen in open
OL,10,Fcourt before celebrating."
OL,12,FHer former husband Mr Hicks, from
OL,13,FSettle, North Yorkshire, added: "Today
OL,14,Ffelt like a hugely important step
OL,15,Fforward."
OL,17,F"We have waited a very long time to
OL,18,Fhear these words from the leadership
OL,19,Fof South Yorkshire Police. What
OL,20,Fmatters now is that the promise made
OL,21,Ftoday is followed through."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]uD@aOUyD@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
