PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FThe commitment comes after years of
OL,8,Flegal efforts by the parents to
OL,9,Fcorrect rulings which state their
OL,10,Fdaughters experienced "swift and
OL,11,Fsudden deaths".
OL,13,FThey are now calling for the
OL,14,Fintroduction of a "Hicks Rule", to
OL,15,Fmake it easier for people in similar
OL,16,Fcircumstances to correct the official
OL,17,Flegal record.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@NO]vD@SOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FNia Williams, partner at Saunders Law
OL,8,F` acting for the Hicks, said: "Jenni
OL,9,FHicks and Trevor Hicks were today able
OL,10,Fto look the Chief Constable in the eye
OL,11,Fand explain why this legal correction
OL,12,Fis so important."
OL,14,F"We are pleased that the Chief
OL,15,FConstable has confirmed that she has
OL,16,Finstructed SYP's legal team to agree
OL,17,Fto the statement in open court and we
OL,18,Fhope that will happen very soon."
OL,26,@pD@_OUvD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772197440
OL,3,CParents of Hillsborough victims
OL,4,Cwelcome police promise to correct
OL,5,Crecords
OL,7,FMs Poultney said: "I'm grateful to
OL,8,Fboth Jenni and Trevor Hicks for
OL,9,Fagreeing to meet with me."
OL,11,F"I'm mindful that I represent an
OL,12,Forganisation which has caused them so
OL,13,Fmuch pain over the years."
OL,15,F"I understand how important it is to
OL,16,Fcorrect the record of the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of the deaths of Vicki
OL,18,Fand Sarah and I have instructed the
OL,19,Fforce's legal team to support the
OL,20,FHicks' legal team in their application
OL,21,Ffor a statement in open court."
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOUwD@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
